::DrillBit::

DrillBit turned to StarScream.
"Yes, the Maximals retreated." He walked off to KitKat's room. He went
in, without knocking, or announcing himself. He went to the bed, and sat
down.
"I'm so sorry, for what you are going through." He hugged her.
